            h4 A two-year PostDoc position open, to join the XAI team in Pisa, Italy
            p.lead.mt-3 Deadline for online applications: #[em Monday, 30 January 2023 at 13:00 CEST]
            p Salary: approximately â‚¬ 3.100 net per month, a competitive salary for Italian standards
